            %i.envelope.outline.icon
            Data Modification
          %a.item{:href => "mailto:support.petlist@gilani.me"}
            %i.envelope.outline.icon
            Support
      .seven.wide.column
        %h4.ui.inverted.header About
        %p
          Hi, I created PetList because after my dog was micro-chipped, I realized I had nowhere to register him. Realizing that I was one of a handful of people skilled enough to create PetList, I did.
        %p
